This directory contains the main "reader" codes for CLAS analysis
method which uses the rootDST files. The reccommended way of using
the codes is by deriving a new class from the TClasTool class, which
then extends the functionality of the class for your own analysis.

If you have any good contributions to these codes, please commit them
to the CVS tree with a descriptive comment. Please start your
own subdirectory, and please also email holtrop@cebaf.gov.

Detailed help can be found at: 

  http://www.physics.unh.edu/maurik/ClasTool.html

----------------------------------------------------------------------
